As the name Megatron is dropped, a strange chord ran through Myrmidon.
He was not sure what it was or how to place it, but it hit him to the
core of his programing. 

&quot;If Megatron is playing diplomat, then perhaps you ought to do the
same.&quot; Even as Myrmidon spoke in an effort to be gruff and commanding,
even as a part of his mind was distracted. &quot;Stand down!&quot; 

Myrmidon watched the others attacking this intruder, even as he tried
to reason with him. He hoped that now the intruder was talking, perhaps
Hyras would call off the other troops . . . especially because Myrmidon
wanted to hear more of Megatron. the words TRUE MEGATRON ringing
through his head like a question. 

Preston
(Myrmidon)

